  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The \"story\" and \"texts\" are puzzle! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a cat puzzle game where you use \"text\" to push the cat. If letter WASD appears in the text, you can push it! You need to push the cat to the goal. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2683570/extras/30225f7d914a5f93c18766c561a945fc.poster.avif?t=1757762493\" width=616 height=219 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2683570/extras/30225f7d914a5f93c18766c561a945fc.webm?t=1757762493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About the Puzzle</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't worry if you can't solve the puzzle. There are in-game hints and solutions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2683570/extras/65e028f88a8d0a4909d7e5aae803a38e.poster.avif?t=1757762493\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2683570/extras/65e028f88a8d0a4909d7e5aae803a38e.webm?t=1757762493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>If you like to solve very difficult puzzles, there are 13 extra challenge levels for you to solve!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2683570/extras/a5cea6801b3de992e74c76737cf04bc4.poster.avif?t=1757762493\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2683570/extras/a5cea6801b3de992e74c76737cf04bc4.webm?t=1757762493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>These levels are intricately crafted with heart and soul.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About the Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do You push cats often?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cat pushing experts believe that it is good for mental health if you push cats every now and then.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, pushing cats is a challenging task. It requires perseverance, patience, and determination. Be prepared physically, mentally and emotionally!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By pushing the cat, you are pushing the cat to think, to remember why they are stuck in this game...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2683570/extras/201fc394569e6e9753665b386714c8b2.poster.avif?t=1757762493\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2683570/extras/201fc394569e6e9753665b386714c8b2.webm?t=1757762493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2683570/extras/201fc394569e6e9753665b386714c8b2.mp4?t=1757762493\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Push the Cat with WASD\" is definitely one of the games ever made!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This \"game\" will try to answer some of the deepest philosophical questions that are very important to humanity and our everyday life, for example:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Why push cat?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Why is cat here?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > What if you can't push the cat? (Oh no!) </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > What is the goal of the cat?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > What is the name of the cat? (Spoilers: It is Push)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Why is cat there?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > What is the conversion of consciousness?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > What is the conversion of consciousness?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > What is the conversion of consciousness?</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2683570/extras/59c6d63ada4009e4be190c32e9a12df2.poster.avif?t=1757762493\" width=616 height=221 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2683570/extras/59c6d63ada4009e4be190c32e9a12df2.webm?t=1757762493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >More About this Game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a game from GMTK Game Jam 2023 with the theme \"roles reversed\". </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The \"story\" and \"texts\" are puzzle! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a cat puzzle game where you use \"text\" to push the cat. If letter WASD appears in the text, you can push it! You need to push the cat to the goal. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2683570/extras/30225f7d914a5f93c18766c561a945fc.poster.avif?t=1757762493\" width=616 height=219 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2683570/extras/30225f7d914a5f93c18766c561a945fc.webm?t=1757762493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About the Puzzle</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't worry if you can't solve the puzzle. There are in-game hints and solutions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2683570/extras/65e028f88a8d0a4909d7e5aae803a38e.poster.avif?t=1757762493\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2683570/extras/65e028f88a8d0a4909d7e5aae803a38e.webm?t=1757762493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>If you like to solve very difficult puzzles, there are 13 extra challenge levels for you to solve!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2683570/extras/a5cea6801b3de992e74c76737cf04bc4.poster.avif?t=1757762493\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_asset