lass=\"bb_paragraph\" > What is the goal of the cat?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > What is the name of the cat? (Spoilers: It is Push)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Why is cat there?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > What is the conversion of consciousness?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > What is the conversion of consciousness?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > What is the conversion of consciousness?</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2683570/extras/59c6d63ada4009e4be190c32e9a12df2.poster.avif?t=1757762493\" width=616 height=221 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2683570/extras/59c6d63ada4009e4be190c32e9a12df2.webm?t=1757762493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >More About this Game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a game from GMTK Game Jam 2023 with the theme \"roles reversed\". </p>",
